OL,3,CFlooded homes in Wales offered council
OL,4,Ctax discount
OL,6,FFlooded households in Wales will be
OL,7,Fable to claim a council tax discount
OL,8,Fas part of an emergency support scheme.
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government has announced
OL,11,Fmore than #2.5 million in funding has
OL,12,Fbeen made available after Storm
OL,13,FClaudia hit the UK on Friday.
OL,15,FSevere conditions resulted in a major
OL,16,Fincident being declared in Monmouth,
OL,17,FSouth Wales, with dozens rescued from
OL,18,Ftheir homes or evacuated after the
OL,19,FRiver Monnow burst its banks.
