OL,3,CFlooded homes in Wales offered council
OL,4,Ctax discount
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has confirmed
OL,7,Ffinancial support will be provided to
OL,8,Fpeople living in Monmouthshire,
OL,9,Fincluding discretionary council tax
OL,10,Freductions for households impacted by
OL,11,Fflooding.
OL,13,FThere will also be grants of #1,000
OL,14,Fand #500 available per home hit by
OL,15,Fflooding, which can be claimed via
OL,16,FMonmouthshire County Council.
