OL,6,FJayne Bryant, Cabinet Secretary for
OL,7,FHousing and Local Government said:
OL,8,F"Monmouthshire Council's response has
OL,9,Fbeen immense in supporting the needs
OL,10,Fof the community following Storm
OL,11,FClaudia.
OL,13,F"I am pleased to be able to confirm
OL,14,Ftoday that the Welsh Government will
OL,15,Fprovide financial support for
OL,16,FMonmouthshire following these
OL,17,Fexceptional events.
