OL,3,CFlooded homes in Wales offered council
OL,4,Ctax discount
OL,6,F"This funding will support costs with
OL,7,Feverything from evacuating people and
OL,8,Fsupplying food to removing household
OL,9,Fwaste and the hire of additional
OL,10,Fvehicles and machinery.
OL,12,F"We will also support the costs of the
OL,13,Fcouncil in giving discretionary
OL,14,Fcouncil tax reductions for those who
OL,15,Fwere flooded.
OL,17,F"Finally, our thoughts are also with
OL,18,Fbusinesses in the centre of Monmouth
OL,19,Fwho have been hard hit.
