OL,6,F"We will also fund the council in
OL,7,Fproviding discretionary reductions in
OL,8,Fnon-domestic rates for affected
OL,9,Fproperties."
OL,11,FMary Ann Brocklesby, Monmouthshire
OL,12,FCounty Council leader, said: "The
OL,13,Fcouncil continues to engage with
OL,14,Fimpacted businesses and residents to
OL,15,Ffully understand the needs arising
OL,16,Ffrom this flooding.
