OL,3,CFlooded homes in Wales offered council
OL,4,Ctax discount
OL,6,F"Following ongoing discussions with
OL,7,FWelsh Government ministers, we are
OL,8,Fdeveloping a scheme for council tax
OL,9,Frelief for residents, non-domestic
OL,10,Frates relief for businesses, and
OL,11,Fgrants to help compensate for costs
OL,12,Fincurred due to the floods.
OL,14,F"Further details on this financial
OL,15,Fsupport will be provided by the end of
OL,16,Fthe week."
