OL,4,Ctax discount
OL,6,FFollowing the flooding in Monmouth,
OL,7,Fall town car parks will be free until
OL,8,Fthe end of December.
OL,10,FAddressing the Welsh Parliament on
OL,11,FTuesday, Climate Change Secretary Huw
OL,12,FIrranca-Davies said current
OL,13,Findications suggest "hundreds" of
OL,14,Fhomes and businesses have been flooded
OL,15,Facross the county of Monmouthshire.
OL,17,F"Seeing the devastation first-hand is
OL,18,Fdeeply sobering, and the impact on
OL,19,Ffamilies and businesses will stay with
OL,20,Fme for many, many years to come," he
OL,21,Fadded.
