OL,6,FHe said homes and businesses had also
OL,7,Fbeen flooded in Caerphilly, Cardiff,
OL,8,FDenbighshire, Newport, Powys, Rhondda
OL,9,FCynon Taf, Torfaen, and the Vale of
OL,10,FGlamorgan, with the full scale of the
OL,11,Fimpact "yet to be determined".
